ARM: S5PV210: Use generic DMA PL330 driver

This patch makes Samsung S5PV210 to use DMA PL330 driver
on DMADEVICE. The S5PV210 uses DMA generic APIs instead of
SAMSUNG specific S3C-PL330 APIs.

